Package curam.util.workflow.supervisor.struct

Contains the class structures used to pass details to and from the infrastructure classes

See:
          Description

Class Summary
BusinessObjectAssociationReservedTasksByUserDetails A structure containing counts of both the open and deferred tasks that have been reserved by a specified user and are associated with a specified case.
BusinessObjectAssociationReservedTasksByUserDetailsList Represents a list of structures containing counts of both the open and deferred tasks that have been reserved by a specified user and are associated with a specified case.
BusinessObjectAssociationReservedTasksByUserKey A structure containing the details required to identify the tasks associated with a specified case.
BusinessObjectAssociationTasksByUserDetails A structure containing the details of a task that is associated with a case.
BusinessObjectAssociationTasksByUserDetailsList A list of structures containing the details of a task that is associated with a case.
BusinessObjectAssociationTasksByUserKey A structure used to identify tasks associated with a case by using the reserved by user name and the status of the task.
BusinessObjectAssociationTasksDetails A structure containing the details of a task.
BusinessObjectAssociationTasksDetailsList A list of structures containing the details of tasks.
BusinessObjectAssociationTasksDueInTheNextMonthKey A structure containing the details required to search for the tasks associated with a specified case and that are due within a specified number of weeks.
BusinessObjectAssociationTasksDueInTheNextTimePeriodDetails A structure containing a task deadline date and a count of all of the reserved and unreserved tasks associated with a specified case that are due on that date.
BusinessObjectAssociationTasksDueInTheNextTimePeriodDetailsList A list of structures containing a task deadline date and a count of all of the reserved and unreserved tasks associated with a specified case that are due on that date.
BusinessObjectAssociationTasksDueInTheNextWeekKey A structure containing the details required to search for the tasks associated with a specified case and that are due within a specified number of days.
BusinessObjectAssociationTasksDueOnDateDetails A structure containing the details of tasks that are associated with a specific case and that are due on the specified date.
BusinessObjectAssociationTasksDueOnDateDetailsList A list of structures containing the details of tasks that are associated with a specific case and that are due on the specified date.
BusinessObjectAssociationTasksDueOnDateKey A structure containing the details required to identify tasks that are associated with a specific case and that are due on a specified date.
BusinessObjectAssociationTasksKey A structure used to identify the tasks associated with a specific case.
 

Package curam.util.workflow.supervisor.struct Description

Contains the class structures used to pass details to and from the infrastructure classes.
